  • java.lang.Object
    • com.guidewire.pl.system.sanitycheck.PreStartupSanityCheck

  • public class PersonalDataEntitySanityCheck
extends com.guidewire.pl.system.sanitycheck.PreStartupSanityCheck
    This class checks that entities tagged 'PersonalData' have valid tag values and implements both Obfuscatable and Obfuscator

      • checkValidityOfPersonalDataTagsOnEntity

        public java.util.List<java.lang.String> checkValidityOfPersonalDataTagsOnEntity(IEntityType entityType)
        Checks that the 'PersonalData' tags on an entity are valid. Returns a list of error messages describing the error, could be empty if there are no errors. Non-persistent and view entities should not be checked.
        Parameters:
        entityType -
        Returns:
        the list of errors, empty if no errors

      • checkEntityImplementObfuscation

        public java.util.List<java.lang.String> checkEntityImplementObfuscation(IEntityType entityType)
        Checks that the entity implements Obfuscator and extends or uses PersonalDataObfuscator. Returns a list of error messages describing the error, could be empty if there are no errors. Delegates, abstract entities, view entities, and non-persistent entities do not need to implement both Obfuscator and Obfuscatable, so are exempted from the check.
        Parameters:
        entityType -
        Returns:
        the list of errors, empty if no errors
